            <h4>Foster better collaboration with hiring managers</h4>
          </div>
          <p>Since all video interviews on Spark Hire are recorded, you can easily share them with hiring managers to obtain their feedback. Whether you're an internal or agency recruiter, getting hiring managers involved earlier on will help you validate decisions on which candidates should be advanced in the hiring process.</p>
          
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-pull-5 laptop"><img src="/img/home/laptop.png" alt="Sharing Video Interviews"></div>
