        <div class="col-sm-5">
          <div class="subHead clearfix">
            <div class="icon"><span class="icon-person-favorite-heart-1-1"></span></div>
            <h4>Improve the quality of your in-person interviews</h4>
          </div>
          <p>Video interview software is an effective tool for helping you identify the best candidates for the position earlier in the hiring process. This ensures you're only investing time and effort into candidates you're confident you want to meet in-person. Get to know your candidates on a more personal level and reap the benefits of high-quality in-person interviews.</p>
          
